481
00:32:14,390 --> 00:32:17,060
Because you don't want me to be happy!

482
00:32:18,603 --> 00:32:20,396
You want to be like you.

483
00:32:21,230 --> 00:32:22,690
No husband.

484
00:32:23,691 --> 00:32:24,943
