495
00:33:23,459 --> 00:33:24,585
No.

496
00:33:25,294 --> 00:33:29,340
I know the feeling of a mother
whose daughter is grieving.

497
00:33:30,091 --> 00:33:31,718
So what, we're twinning, is that it?

498
00:33:33,011 --> 00:33:34,721
Come on, Mercy, just stop it.

499
00:33:35,847 --> 00:33:40,018
