because my daughter is already a widow.

500
00:33:40,435 --> 00:33:42,687
Why are you thinking that way?

501
00:33:44,272 --> 00:33:47,108
Maybe it's because you were like that
when Sam became a widow.

502
00:33:47,775 --> 00:33:49,068
Did you enjoy that?

503
00:33:49,152 --> 00:33:51,654
You know, you're such a bad person.

504
00:33:51,738 --> 00:33:53,239
