00:36:23,014 --> 00:36:24,223
- You're too much!
- Mother, that's enough!

539
00:36:24,307 --> 00:36:25,892
- You're the one who's too much!
- Ms. Ruth, that's enough!

540
00:36:25,975 --> 00:36:27,185
- Come here, oh gosh!
- Mother!

541
00:36:27,268 --> 00:36:28,436
Ma'am, stop it.

542
00:36:28,519 --> 00:36:30,438
No matter what happens,
you always blame us!

543
00:36:30,521 --> 00:36:31,564
Why are you meddling?

544
00:36:31,647 --> 00:36:33,482
- You're too much!
- You!

545
00:36:33,566 --> 00:36:37,737
I don't need any concern coming from
your family, Mercy!

546
00:36:37,820 --> 00:36:41,199
I don't need it, especially not from you!

547
00:36:42,658 --> 00:36:44,076
Damn you!

548
00:36:44,744 --> 00:36:46,078
- You're too much!
- My goodness!

549
00:36:46,162 --> 00:36:46,954
You're worse!

550
00:36:47,038 --> 00:36:48,456
Stop bothering me!

551
00:36:48,956 --> 00:36:50,208
You're too much!

552
00:36:54,962 --> 00:36:55,755
Mother…

553
00:36:55,838 --> 00:36:57,757
That woman is annoying.

554
00:36:59,634 --> 00:37:00,927
All of you…

555
00:37:02,220 --> 00:37:03,721
One day you'll get what you deserve!

556
00:37:03,804 --> 00:37:05,973
One day you will too!

557
00:37:15,149 --> 00:37:16,359
Why did you follow me here?

558
00:37:16,442 --> 00:37:18,736
You have no business being here!

559
00:37:19,403 --> 00:37:21,197
Hey, George!

560
00:37:25,243 --> 00:37:27,787
Sam is a Palacios. She's family.

561
00:37:27,870 --> 00:37:30,373
There's nothing wrong with her being here.

562
00:37:33,709 --> 00:37:35,503
Are you okay, Sam?

563
00:37:35,586 --> 00:37:36,921
How's my grandchild?

564
00:37:38,089 --> 00:37:39,632
- Okay, come on sit down.
- Okay.

565
00:37:40,549 --> 00:37:42,009
- Have a seat.
- I'm okay.

566
00:37:42,093 --> 00:37:43,594
It's normal.

567
00:37:43,678 --> 00:37:44,804
It was just fatigue.

568
00:37:44,887 --> 00:37:45,972
That's great.

569
00:37:46,055 --> 00:37:47,306
Come on, sit down.

570
00:37:56,607 --> 00:38:00,111
Doc, what were the results
of Basil's lab test?

571
00:38:00,194 --> 00:38:02,321
What really killed my husband?

572
00:38:16,252 --> 00:38:20,464
These are the initial results
although not yet conclusive.

573
00:38:20,548 --> 00:38:23,175
We still need to do the autopsy first

574
00:38:23,259 --> 00:38:24,593
to further confirm.

575
00:38:24,677 --> 00:38:26,137
Just tell us.

576
00:38:28,014 --> 00:38:29,098
Okay.

577
00:38:29,181 --> 00:38:33,019
We found massive amounts
of morphine in Basil's system.

578
00:38:33,102 --> 00:38:35,021
What?

579
00:38:35,104 --> 00:38:36,314
Morphine?

580
00:38:36,397 --> 00:38:41,068
Massive amounts of morphine
indicating foul play.

581
00:38:41,152 --> 00:38:44,530
There's no amount that would indicate
that this is not accidental.

582
00:38:46,949 --> 00:38:48,159
This was deliberate.

583
00:38:49,118 --> 00:38:50,953
Someone did this to my husband.

584
00:38:53,205 --> 00:38:54,915
Basil is allergic to morphine.

585
00:38:54,999 --> 00:38:57,126
He wouldn't just take it on purpose.

586
00:38:59,962 --> 00:39:02,048
Someone poisoned my husband.

587
00:39:02,131 --> 00:39:05,092
- Who did this to him?!
- George, calm down.

588
00:39:05,176 --> 00:39:07,720
I'll have this investigated!

589
00:39:07,803 --> 00:39:10,806
We need to know who did this to Basil!

590
00:39:10,890 --> 00:39:13,893
The person who poisoned
my husband will pay!

591
00:39:59,188 --> 00:40:01,899
I will look for the person
who poisoned you.

592
00:40:03,234 --> 00:40:04,777
I promise.

593
00:40:14,912 --> 00:40:15,913
Pa…

594
00:40:22,086 --> 00:40:23,421
I can't, George.

595
00:40:26,048 --> 00:40:27,550
I don't want to see him.

596
00:40:28,134 --> 00:40:29,927
I don't want to accept that he's gone.

597
00:40:32,138 --> 00:40:33,389
I can't, George.

598
00:40:34,306 --> 00:40:35,558
I can't do it.

599
00:40:36,434 --> 00:40:37,351
I can't do it.

600
00:40:43,399 --> 00:40:45,234
Pa, I know it's difficult.

601
00:40:45,776 --> 00:40:47,236
Look at me, please.

602
00:40:51,699 --> 00:40:52,992
But you can do it.

603
00:40:54,660 --> 00:40:56,287
I'll go with you.

604
00:41:45,002 --> 00:41:46,712
Basil, son, I know you're in pain,

605
00:41:46,795 --> 00:41:49,381
but the doctor's coming
with the medicine, okay?

606
00:41:49,465 --> 00:41:52,009
He's going to give you
the medicine, all right?

607
00:41:52,092 --> 00:41:53,135
Okay?

608
00:42:07,107 --> 00:42:08,442
Doc, what's happening?

609
00:42:09,026 --> 00:42:10,402
What's taking you so long?

610
00:42:10,486 --> 00:42:13,822
My son is in pain.
Why don't you give him a painkiller?

611
00:42:14,615 --> 00:42:16,909
I'm sorry, Mr. Palacios,

612
00:42:16,992 --> 00:42:23,415
but Basil's intradermal test result showed
that he is allergic to painkillers.

613
00:42:23,499 --> 00:42:26,752
We have alternative methods
that we are considering.

614
00:42:26,835 --> 00:42:29,463
All right. Whatever it is,
just give it to him.

615
00:42:29,547 --> 00:42:32,424
- He's in pain. Hurry up, please.
- Okay, we will, we will.

616
00:42:39,223 --> 00:42:41,308
Son, the doctor's coming back, okay?

617
00:42:41,392 --> 00:42:44,061
He's going to give you the medicine, okay?

618
00:42:44,144 --> 00:42:46,522
It's okay, Pa.

619
00:42:46,605 --> 00:42:48,232
I can take pain.

620
00:42:48,315 --> 00:42:52,194
And I'm a strong and brave boy.

621
00:42:52,278 --> 00:42:53,779
I know you're…

622
00:42:53,862 --> 00:42:55,739
I know you're a brave boy.

623
00:42:55,823 --> 00:42:57,157
I know you're strong.

624
00:42:57,241 --> 00:42:58,659
All right?

625
00:42:58,742 --> 00:42:59,910
Okay, Basil?

626
00:43:00,369 --> 00:43:02,663
Okay? You just hang on, okay?

627
00:43:02,746 --> 00:43:04,039
- Okay.
- All right.

628
00:43:07,459 --> 00:43:11,297
You grew up to be a strong and brave man
that you are, son.

629
00:43:13,424 --> 00:43:14,633
Please…

630
00:43:14,717 --> 00:43:15,843
Who…

631
00:43:16,844 --> 00:43:17,928
who…

632
00:43:19,263 --> 00:43:21,599
who did this to you?!

633
00:43:23,142 --> 00:43:24,226
Who?

634
00:43:25,185 --> 00:43:27,062
Who poisoned him?

635
00:43:27,146 --> 00:43:28,147
Who?

636
00:43:36,322 --> 00:43:38,449
Sam, why are you hurrying?

637
00:43:38,532 --> 00:43:39,533
Be careful.

638
00:43:39,617 --> 00:43:40,951
You're carrying my grandchild.

639
00:43:41,035 --> 00:43:43,287
That child is the future
of Palacios Mining.

640
00:43:43,370 --> 00:43:44,788
That child will succeed me.

641
00:43:44,872 --> 00:43:45,956
Really, Aurora?

642
00:43:46,040 --> 00:43:47,583
My son, Basil, just died,

643
00:43:47,666 --> 00:43:49,543
and you're still thinking about
the company?

644
00:43:49,627 --> 00:43:50,878
"If you outlive me."

645
00:43:50,961 --> 00:43:53,255
That's the last thing you told Basil.

646
00:43:53,339 --> 00:43:57,051
You didn't want my son to outlive you.
It's you who poisoned him.

647
00:43:57,134 --> 00:43:58,510
<i>Is what Mother and I heard true?</i>

648
00:43:58,594 --> 00:44:00,304
It was morphine that poisoned Basil?

649
00:44:00,387 --> 00:44:01,930
Morphine, just like my medicine?

650
00:44:02,473 --> 00:44:07,227
Could it be that George has known for
a long time that Basil had a mistress,

651
00:44:07,311 --> 00:44:10,689
and that's the reason why
she killed her husband?

652
00:44:10,773 --> 00:44:17,780
George is a bitter, vengeful wife
who killed her own husband.

653
00:44:18,364 --> 00:44:19,406
I need your help.

654
00:44:19,490 --> 00:44:21,075
NEXT EPISODE
